    "title": "אֶבֶן הָרֹאשָׁה | Even haRoshah (\"The corner stone\"), a seliḥah for the Fast of Tevet attributed to Avraham bar Menaḥem (13th c.)",
    "author": "Aharon N. Varady (transcription)",
